Yes! It's a top secret thing that would make FBI agents go after him!

18
00:01:01,552 --> 00:01:03,222
You'd better watch out!

19
00:01:05,176 --> 00:01:06,936
A top secret thing...?

20
00:01:07,917 --> 00:01:10,121
Metal Breath... pickup...

21
00:01:18,499 --> 00:01:20,223
