Hey, why is he acting so weird?

33
00:02:29,942 --> 00:02:31,748
Secret? With Jun?

34
00:02:32,32 --> 00:02:34,391
Mhm. Do you know anything?

35
00:02:34,391 --> 00:02:36,524
Oh, uh...

36
00:02:38,673 --> 00:02:39,654
Attack!

37
00:02:44,215 --> 00:02:45,378
Let's go!

38
00:02:45,619 --> 00:02:47,275
You got it, Blue Cop!

39
00:02:47,443 --> 00:02:49,327
Seal complete!

40
00:02:49,394 --> 00:02:51,752
I might say... uh...

41
00:02:51,752 --> 00:02:53,996
What is it, Theo?! Tell me!

42
00:02:53,996 --> 00:02:55,648
Actually, actually...

43
00:02:55,888 --> 00:02:57,834
Well Jun is...

44
00:02:57,834 --> 00:02:59,37
Yeah?

45
00:02:59,37 --> 00:03:00,829
It's his birthday today!

46
00:03:00,829 --> 00:03:03,995
Oh-aha! That was it?

47
00:03:03,995 --> 00:03:05,668
Y-Yeah, that's it...

48
00:03:05,668 --> 00:03:09,885
Oh, Theo, you should have told me! I misunderstood!

49
00:03:09,885 --> 00:03:12,130
Then... we should go celebrate!

50
00:03:12,130 --> 00:03:13,550
...celebrate?

51
00:03:13,550 --> 00:03:17,566
Yes! We should get a cake and go to Jun's right now!

52
00:03:17,566 --> 00:03:19,877
S-shouldn't we call before we go-

53
00:03:19,877 --> 00:03:25,266
But that's no fun! I'm sure Jun would like a surprise event too!

54
00:03:25,266 --> 00:03:28,655
Oh no, this does not feel good...

55
00:03:33,933 --> 00:03:38,468
It's my birthday and I'm mowing the lawn!!

56
00:03:38,468 --> 00:03:42,462
Mom, Dad, everyone, I'm not feeling loved today...

57
00:03:42,462 --> 00:03:44,420
Jun, what are you up to?

58
00:03:44,420 --> 00:03:46,480
Can't you see? I'm mowing the lawn!

59
00:03:46,480 --> 00:03:50,164
Looks fun! Can I try? Please, I wanna try!

60
00:03:55,122 --> 00:03:56,957
Woohoo!

61
00:03:57,12 --> 00:03:58,563
Is it fun?

62
00:03:59,409 --> 00:04:01,682
Haha! It's the best!

63
00:04:03,338 --> 00:04:06,205
Hey, Jun! Let me do something, Jun!

64
00:04:12,325 --> 00:04:14,688
Haha! This is fun!

65
00:04:14,826 --> 00:04:15,285
Woohoo!

66
00:04:15,285 --> 00:04:17,972
I'm happy that you guys are happy...

67
00:04:18,95 --> 00:04:19,94
Jun.

68
00:04:20,335 --> 00:04:23,484
What if someone sees them? We agreed that Metal Cardbots should be a secret.

69
00:04:23,484 --> 00:04:25,644
That's true...

70
00:04:27,135 --> 00:04:29,533
Ah, Blue Cop! Come here and help me!

71
00:04:29,605 --> 00:04:31,140
But don't let anyone see you!

72
00:04:31,943 --> 00:04:34,792
Hey buddy, wasn't the food today the worst- huh?

73
00:04:36,31 --> 00:04:40,180
This street has been closed. Please use the other street.

74
00:04:40,180 --> 00:04:41,200
Let's just go play games.

75
00:04:41,200 --> 00:04:42,780
Yeah, I agree... let's go.

76
00:04:44,50 --> 00:04:46,480
...should we really be doing this?

77
00:04:46,480 --> 00:04:48,690
Come on. Nothing is going to happen. Just relax.

78
00:04:51,689 --> 00:04:53,285
Oh, excuse me!

79
00:04:53,611 --> 00:04:55,870
I'm sorry, this area is out of bounds.

80
00:04:55,870 --> 00:04:56,890
...huh?

81
00:04:56,944 --> 00:05:01,605
Hi, I'm sorry, but we just need to get over there. Could you just let us through?

82
00:05:01,605 --> 00:05:05,485
But, uh... well, uh...

83
00:05:05,485 --> 00:05:08,6
Oh, it's you!

84
00:05:08,6 --> 00:05:11,233
Perhaps... you could go ask the person... in charge?

85
00:05:11,233 --> 00:05:14,417
Oh, haha, right. Hold on a minute!

86
00:05:15,727 --> 00:05:18,202
Okay, let them through!

87
00:05:18,202 --> 00:05:19,472
What's going on?

88
00:05:19,472 --> 00:05:21,84
Theo has come over.

89
00:05:25,179 --> 00:05:26,271
Waah!

90
00:05:26,687 --> 00:05:27,980
Hello!

91
00:05:28,454 --> 00:05:30,164
H-Hey Anna!

92
00:05:30,655 --> 00:05:32,413
Hey, this is an emergency! Hurry, transform!

93
00:05:32,413 --> 00:05:34,971
Oh no, this is bad!

94
00:05:34,971 --> 00:05:37,788
Sorry for dropping in like this. Is this a bad time?

95
00:05:37,788 --> 00:05:41,439
Nonono! Of course not! You guys are always welcome here!

96
00:05:41,439 --> 00:05:44,161
That's good! What were you up to?

97
00:05:44,161 --> 00:05:46,820
Uh... cleaning the garden?

98
00:05:46,820 --> 00:05:48,427
Wow! Can I see?

99
00:05:48,427 --> 00:05:53,363
B-b-b-but Anna! I-It's not done yet!

100
00:05:54,906 --> 00:05:56,960
